The paper proposes a novel face recognition method using deep neural networks, which is a common topic in computer vision (cs.CV). The method involves capturing pairwise relations between local appearance patches, which is a learning task that falls under machine learning (cs.LG) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI). The paper also evaluates the proposed method on face datasets, which is a common task in multimedia (cs.MM) and computer security (cs.CR).
